                    style: new TextStyle(fontSize: 30.0),
                  ),
                )
              ],
            ),
            new Row(
              mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
              children: <Widget>[
                Expanded(
                  child: Padding(
                    padding: const EdgeInsets.only(
